Rating: 4
This is amazing. I doubled the recipe and used 11x17 glass dish. My only issue was the "dough" which was more like sticky biscuit dough. I had helpers and they added all if the milk at once. That may have caused the sticky problem. No idea how one could roll out the dough... I just dropped it on the top in 8 piles and sprinkled turbino sugar on top. Adults and kids loved this cobbler.

